g.text: a) Place 2 HGR15R rails on the C beam
and align the holes to match the mounting rack
b) Pay attention not to touch
unnecessary areas on the C beam with oily hands
c) Loosely tighten the 10 screws ""allow for free play""

g.onmousemove: ShowToolTip(evt,'5',"0257_M4x14 Socket head cap screw black")
